            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Extremely pure natural nickel (purity 99.9%) foils were",
                "cut into round shaped (diam. 12 mm) and cleaned",
                "thoroughly by acetone. Masses of the foils were in the",
                "range 0.6675-0.7006g. Each of the foils was sandwiched",
